Package ca.openosp.openo.casemgmt.web

Class NoteDisplayNonNote

java.lang.Object
ca.openosp.openo.casemgmt.web.NoteDisplayNonNote
All Implemented Interfaces:
NoteDisplay
public class NoteDisplayNonNote extends Object implements NoteDisplay
The echart seems to have non-note items in the note list. As a result this class will hold non-note items. A constructor can be made for each type of non-note item.
